reviewText: Not anything you would want to spend your money on... very disappointing.
Its great I'm learning alot from it.  I hope to be healing myself very soon. I  love it very much

This DVD will most likely not be what you are looking for on the topics in its title.
Productions values are poor and the speaker has annoying coughing spells.
Intellectual stuff but title is deceptive as to the content on the DVD.
This is a great presentation aimed at the enlightened individual. I've watched a few of these videos and taken classes and this is definitely world class instruction.
